bioContent.line: Born and raised in the Pacific Northwest, I am now a sophmore at Rice University studying Computer Science and Mathematics.
I enjoy computer science because it gives me the opportunity to solve the problems I witness using a combination of creative and strategic problem solving.
I am passionate about computer science and mathematics and I am always looking for new opportunities to explore these subjects and gain new experience with them.
I know Python, Java, and C/C++ as well as JavaScript, HTML, CSS, and React, and have completed projects using all of these languages.
